text: Aldo Stella (born August 9, 1930) was an Italian football Goalkeeper who played in Egypt for Al-Masry and Zamalek. ==Personal life== Aldo is the younger cousin of Ettore Moscatelli. ==Honors== ;Zamalek SC: *Egyptian Premier League: (1) *: 1959–60 *Egypt Cup: (4) *: 1957–58, 1958–59, 1959–60, 1961–62 ==References== Category:Al Masry SC players Category:Zamalek SC players Category:1930 births Category:Living people Category:Sportspeople from Port Said Category:Egyptian Premier League players Category:Association football goalkeepers Category:Italian footballers Category:Italian expatriate footballers Category:Expatriate footballers in Egypt
